## Limitations
The information provided in this report is based on available online resources and may not capture all the nuances of the programs or the latest updates. Additionally, eligibility criteria and program availability can change, so it is advisable for individuals to contact the relevant agencies directly for the most current information. Furthermore, the effectiveness of these programs in addressing the needs of all eligible Texans was not assessed in this report.